# TownSuite.ConvertionServer
A server with a simple API for converting data from one type to another.


# Example 

Send a base64 encoded pdf and returns a base 64 encoded png.

```bash
curl --location --request POST 'http://127.0.0.1/PdfConverter' \
--header 'Authorization: Basic [the base 64 credentials]' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
    "data": ""
}'
```
